  "remarks": "Battery Company Rigel JSC is a manufacturer of nickel-metal hydride and silver-zinc batteries, and has been a supplier to the Russian navy for more than 15 years. The company describes itself as “a leading developer of lithium-ion batteries and batteries for autonomous and uninterruptible power systems, communications, transport, and other equipment” and provides a full cycle of development, production, and supply of lithium batteries for the Russian Navy and the Russian Ministry of Defence.",
